author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, President Trump confronts the anti-white president of South Africa in the Oval Office. The “No Tax On Tips” bill passes through the Senate unanimously, which means it’s a really bad idea. Trans activists figure out a way to shove their propaganda in your face, even out in the middle of the wilderness. And a school employee in Oregon is accused of a “biased incident” because he had a copy of my children’s book, Johnny the Walrus, on his shelf.
